cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NA, cs.IT, cs.SI 

The paper deals with learning-based iterative methods for inverse problems in statistics, learning, and vision areas. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). The paper also discusses scheduling policies and convergence behaviors, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI).
